workflows.name: Glean probe-scraper
workflows.display_title: VPN-4676: Use Conda for all Apple builds (#6734)

head_commit.message:
VPN-4676: Use Conda for all Apple builds (#6734)

* Fix golang build artifacts
* Try using a job_pool for cargo jobs to prevent waiting on package locks
* Fix rustlang build artifacts
* Attempt universal building with Conda
* Pass compiler down to sentry
* Remove MacOS/universal taskcluster job
* Use Conda for iOS too?
* Fix build artifact tarball on iOS
* Fix wireguard-go compilation on MacOS
* Fix linker warnings about MacOS version mismatch
* Bump CMake version to 3.25
* Add iOS Rust targets to Conda environment
* Use cctools package instead of forcing the compiler
